pygtk_image

I am trying to use pygtk to show images of simplecv/opencv instead of pygame.
pygtk_image contains a class DisplayImage. I am calling gtk.main() using threads.

Example:
>>> i = Image("lenna")
>>> d = DisplayImage()
>>> d.show(i.toRGB().getBitmap())
>>> time.sleep(5)
>>> d.quit()

Some other examples are added.
